rComments: She is truly the ideal professor. My writing was only worth about a C when I started the class, but in the end I received an A. She is the reason why my writing became so much better as the year progressed. It was her who taught me how to succeed in English. Also, she is incredibly sweet and funny during class. Absolutely an amazing professor.

Professor Gniadek is an extremely passionate and delightful prof. There are many ways to improve your grade and she provides clear advice on improving your writing. My writing was average at best but her thoughtful criticisms guided my writing to a more complex analysis without making me feel stupid.

ENG250Y is a course that allows you to feel the valor of hard-work. You will genuinely learn and remember insights and beautiful quotations from novels and stories. The writing pieces and longer essays will allow you to articulate with brio and elevation. This course will actually teach students something and you can take knowledge away at the end.
